comments: Carter Jr. (CHI) firms up in a screening position in Ntilikina's (NYK) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Barrett (NYK) has a hand/forearm to Satoransky's (CHI) front during the drive but the contact does not affect his SQBR.
Carter Jr. (CHI) is firming up in a screening position in Ntilikina's (NYK) path and absorbs the contact.
Portis (NYK) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by LaVine (CHI).
Carter Jr. (CHI) firms up in a screening position and absorbs the contact from Morris Sr. (NYK).
Barrett (NYK) and Satoransky (CHI) engage and separate during the rebound.
LaVine (CHI) grabs Barrett's (NYK) jersey and pulls it away from his body on his drive to the basket.
Morris Sr. (NYK) extends his leg as part of a natural shooting motion on the jump shot attempt and the contact with Satoransky (CHI) is incidental.
Barrett (NYK) commits a take foul on LaVine (CHI).
During the inbound, LaVine (CHI) briefly places one hand on Barrett's (NYK) hip but he does not apply any force or affect his SQBR.

Markkanen (CHI) makes contact with the loose ball but it is not a controlled dribble.  He then reestablishes himself in bounds before legally making contact with the ball again and gathering the loose ball.
Satoransky (CHI) tries to commit a take foul on Ntilikina (NYK) but the contact is marginal.
Carter Jr. (CHI) commits a take foul on Barrett (NYK).
Carter Jr. (CHI) and Ntilikina (NYK) briefly engage with one another during the screen.
Barrett (NYK) and Satoransky (CHI) engage and separate during the rebound.
Satoransky (CHI) commits a take foul on Barrett (NYK).
Randle (NYK) and Markkanen (CHI) both go for the rebound and Randle cleanly tips the ball out.
